\cf0 Interview & getting the job\
- interview questions, a few gems\
- things to look out for\
- good questions to ask the interviewer\
- don't sign right away\
- think about it\
- know your salary expectations, some companies will have a range in mind you have to live too so don't sell yourself short\
\
